				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/B%E1%BB%93i-B%C3%B9i-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-%C4%91%C4%83ng-Nh%E1%BA%A1c-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-l%C3%A2u/poem-4zxKo0iDatCbKaFIdz1otQ">Bồi Bùi sứ quân đăng Nhạc Dương lâu - 陪裴使君登岳陽樓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Quang-Vi%E1%BB%87n/B%C3%BAt-Nghi%E1%BB%85n-s%C6%A1n/poem-BpUQrNK0j_0uFrkKmfaLcA">Bút Nghiễn sơn - 筆研山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Quang-Vi%E1%BB%87n/author-S_xuWCLlS-Q1f7XHRjwz3w">Lê Quang Viện</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%C4%83ng/C%E1%BB%95-th%E1%BB%83-thi-nh%E1%BA%A5t-th%E1%BB%A7-ho%E1%BA%A1-Tri%E1%BB%81u-Ti%C3%AAn-qu%E1%BB%91c-s%E1%BB%A9-L%C3%BD-%C4%90%E1%BA%A9u-Phong-k%C3%BD-gi%E1%BA%A3n-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-thi%C3%AAn/poem-dufjwR7ke5zeT0Pc19PDnw">Cổ thể thi nhất thủ hoạ Triều Tiên quốc sứ Lý Đẩu Phong ký giản trường thiên - 古體詩一首和朝鮮國使李斗峰寄柬長篇</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%C4%83ng/author-9vK1MaRfv_HUDMyHo1xP_w">Nguyễn Đăng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ph%C3%BAc-L%C3%A2m/C%C3%B4-th%C3%B4n-mao-x%C3%A1/poem-0gILsjG3aMV1229nji2beA">Cô thôn mao xá - 孤村茅舍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Ph%C3%BAc-L%C3%A2m/author-kjKBPKP3VM3yjyBJUH1Xkw">Ngô Phúc Lâm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/C%C3%BAc-hoa-b%C3%A1ch-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-JnZygAQIDZoWSWGuo-DRzg">Cúc hoa bách vịnh kỳ 2 - 菊花百詠其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/author-8OezdZDSC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A1nh-H%E1%BB%B7-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/%C4%90%C3%A1p-Ph%C3%A1p-Dung-s%E1%BA%AFc-kh%C3%B4ng-ph%C3%A0m-th%C3%A1nh-chi-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-OdqTESAKnmtAntHKKOT8yg">Đáp Pháp Dung sắc không, phàm thánh chi vấn - 答法融色空凡聖之問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%C3%A1nh-H%E1%BB%B7-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-bHJh7yXSuJ5LfQpC8X5xEw">Khánh Hỷ thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/%C4%90%C3%ACnh-ti%E1%BB%81n-tr%C3%BAc/poem-wsYsfjO3QLdNWt6az1N0cA">Đình tiền trúc - 庭前竹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%C3%B9ng-Kh%E1%BA%AFc-Khoan/author-Pf4dpRXbHmTjs-pG65imRA">Phùng Khắc Khoan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-Ng%C3%A0n-xu%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99ng/poem-EbHtVJXyXk_A3XCIsYLE9A">Đông Ngàn xuân mộng - 東岸春夢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/L%E1%BB%87-giang-nh%C3%A0n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh/poem-wDJ3K_TuhlzxZ_C2oTiUMg">Lệ giang nhàn vịnh - 麗江閑咏</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Ti%E1%BB%83u-vi%C3%AAn-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-NdBxm1jjdJsfKXxSMcJR8w">Tiểu viên kỳ 1 - 小園其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
